    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new without the showroom price tag? This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredibly good care of it, and it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. You won't find a single blemish on this gem. It's super smooth, reliable, and ready for its next adventure with you. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
