    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering, presented in collector-grade condition. The S54B32 inline-six engine maintains exceptional compression across all cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam phasing and throttle response. The Getrag Type D 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a subframe that has been inspected for structural integrity and shows no signs of stress-induced fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics, featuring fresh bushings and dampers that preserve the vehicle's legendary lateral acceleration and torsional rigidity. All fluid reservoirs, cooling system components, and heat shielding are in pristine state, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule and a climate-controlled history. This is a mechanically transparent vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
