    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent; the leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing zero bolster wear or creasing. All electronics, switches, and displays function with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy, including recent fluid services and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The undercarriage is as clean as the engine bay, showing no signs of road debris or weather exposure. Included with the sale are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one. This vehicle is for the buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
